@startuml UC-07_Export_Report

title UC-07: Export Usage Report - Sequence Diagram

skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #0288D1
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #E1F5FE
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

actor User
participant Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant AnalyticsService
participant Database as DB
participant "Export Service" as ExportSvc
participant "Cloud Storage" as Storage

User -> Frontend: 1. Click "Export Report"
Frontend -> User: 2. Show format options (PDF/CSV/Excel)
User -> Frontend: 3. Select format & date range
Frontend -> API: 4. POST /api/v1/analytics/export
API -> AnalyticsService: 5. generate_report(user_id, format, period)
AnalyticsService -> DB: 6. Query all analytics data
DB --> AnalyticsService: 7. Complete dataset
AnalyticsService -> ExportSvc: 8. format_report(data, format)
ExportSvc --> ExportSvc: 9. Generate document (PDF/CSV/Excel)
ExportSvc --> AnalyticsService: 10. File bytes
AnalyticsService -> Storage: 11. Upload report
Storage --> AnalyticsService: 12. File URL
AnalyticsService -> DB: 13. Log export event
DB --> AnalyticsService: 14. Logged
AnalyticsService --> API: 15. Return {download_url, file_name}
API --> Frontend: 16. 200 OK + download link
Frontend --> User: 17. Provide download link

@enduml
